{"tid":1639420,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[南美] 光復香港 到 復活島！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:03:39.000Z","uid":4512,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bba276692e84fb3bba8143c82605893cd30741","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"話說朋友一早計劃好去幾個月南美旅行，出發前就爆發反送中，朋友知道自己要離開香港都感到囉囉攣<br />\n<br />\n我就提議「喂點解唔帶支光復香港旗去旅行呢？」<br />\n朋友就自己整咗支旗帶埋上路<br />\n<br />\n好多同路人都帶咗支旗去世界各地，但係今次<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將光復香港帶到復活島</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DBcYr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DBcYr1.jpg&h=d90e2643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港依家真係好撚黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望香港有一日會 光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvEmRND.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvEmRND.jpg&h=5e3d1398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJm07kZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJm07kZ.jpg&h=4a0a9a07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KstVWek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKstVWek.jpg&h=2bfb2055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家出去海外玩既時候，都把握機會同外國人講下香港既情況，親身講一次勝過睇十份廣告<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"49b72c00368ae65d1cdc32a2b54174af15876129","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTAhqbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTAhqbC.jpg&h=4fbab2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解出唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2Nr2Yh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2Nr2Yh.jpg&h=6ff0502c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vYbuDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vYbuDi.jpg&h=746411d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sn2SYwD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsn2SYwD.jpg&h=52ff289f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9b30665b3f1071e28eb796fb6fe128b9955a4a2","tid":1639420,"uid":50880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"前線勇武手足好需要呢樣野，你知道嗎？我地係咪冇工程部？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"521ea77cf07ab6ac216c0cf7d5b5e872c3f68971","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a037217df5d9d6c260cfa1b69c1d2133e3f713a5","tid":1639420,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93715a05d1dd6c4e31e2f5d93fb65cc5707027d5","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:38:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6527d8faa9c4267c6b190905277d41ea4f794b1","tid":1639420,"uid":264555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"喵喵喵喵 喵喵喵喵！"},{"pid":"4fc285ee08345f0fe9a689934f24076898d771d7","tid":1639420,"uid":295621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"光復