plyTime":"2019-10-10T20:54:07.000Z","msg":"要人！科大要科大人！！<br />\n班nds推左個黨員選入校董會<br />\n選到既話佢地諗住收窄學生會既權力<br />\n之後滲多啲自己人入去，定啲措施幫助ust大陸人<br />\n<br />\n讀緊科大嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n班大陸人靜靜雞係wechat吹哂雞去左投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係朋友圈推得好行，但好似冇咩local留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c3c10d239a2b4dd14a8498e20adec65f028e18","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba10b79b7a247c41438e71fd58fb681c6883877b","tid":1639420,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:51:59.000Z","msg":"嗰邊多唔多支那人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"我朋友去左好多地方<br />\n<br />\n喺阿根廷最南 ushuaia 見過跟團既大陸人好嘈<br />\n喺復活島就見過一堆超過20人既，但都係廿幾歲，相對正常"},{"pid":"592130c158e28273a964918d7e113fb95a92cd12","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aec8c10e462c4097782e008aa1d0783337421e7c","tid":1639420,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49b72c00368ae65d1cdc32a2b54174af15876129","tid":1639420,"uid":4512,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTAhqbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTAhqbC.jpg&h=4fbab2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解出唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2Nr2Yh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2Nr2Yh.jpg&h=6ff0502c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vYbuDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vYbuDi.jpg&h=746411d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sn2SYwD.jpg\" d